headline: State Street to Speak at the Morgan Stanley U.S. Financials Conference
summary: BOSTON, May 30, 2025--State Street Corporation (NYSE: STT) announced today that its Chairman & Chief Executive Officer, Ron O’Hanley, and its interim Chief Financial Officer, Mark Keating, will present at the Morgan Stanley U.S. Financials Conference in New York, NY on Wednesday, June 11, 2025 at approximately 9:00 am ET.

headline: US Treasuries Set for First Monthly Loss of 2025 on Deficit Woes
summary: (Bloomberg) -- US Treasuries are on track to deliver their first monthly loss this year, buffeted by renewed tariff uncertainty and growing anxiety over mounting levels of government debt.
